parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbags not deploying in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the instrument panel
the airbag light stays on
the airbag light flickers on and off
the airbag system is inoperative
the airbag sensor is faulty
the airbag light remains illuminated after repair attempts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, catch fire, or experience various electrical malfunctions, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The service engine light illuminates
the vehicle stalls or hesitates
the horn is difficult to locate
the interior of the vehicle catches on fire
the electrical system malfunctions
and the vehicle experiences issues with starting.
